    class=&#34;gallery-image&#34;
    data-flex-grow=&#34;160&#34;
    data-flex-basis=&#34;384px&#34;
  
/&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img
  src=&#34;https://zeroszhang.github.io/p/%E7%BA%A2%E9%BB%91%E6%A0%91/assets/PixPin_2025-05-11_17-05-15_l7RxXM2Rc_.gif&#34;
